         <abstract>
            <p>
               The Prayer of St Mary on 21 Sane on the mount of Golgotha
               (variants: 20<hi rend="apices">th</hi>, 24<hi rend="apices">th</hi>, 25<hi rend="apices">th</hi> Sane) is one of the
               prayers included in the printed <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2701Dawit"/>.
              It contains formulas against evil whose efficacy is guaranteed through Jesus Christ.     
              Some manuscripts mention as the author <persName ref="PRS7953Prochoru">Prochorus</persName>.
                </p>
         </abstract>
